":45,"featured":true,"imageUrl":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1531415074968-036ba1b575da?w=1200&h=500&fit=crop&q=80","description":"The ICC T20 World Cup 2026 gets underway at the world's largest cricket stadium — the magnificent Narendra Modi Stadium in Ahmedabad, home to 132,000 fans. Twenty20 cricket at its very best: explosive batting, stunning catches and nail-biting finishes as the finest white-ball cricketers on the planet compete for the global title. This opening match sets the stage for four weeks of unmissable cricket across the subcontinent.","partners":[{"partnerId":"footballticketnet","partnerName":"FootballTicketNet","partnerIcon":"⚽","price":45,"tag":"Best Price"},{"partnerId":"awin","partnerName":"Awin","partnerIcon":"🌐","price":52}]},{"id":"23","slug":"t20-world-cup-2026-india-vs-pakistan","sport":"cricket","leagueSlug":"t20-world-cup","eventName":"T20 World Cup 2026 — India vs Pakistan","league":"ICC T20 World Cup","date":"2026-02-22","time":"19:00","venue":"Eden Gardens","city":"Kolkata, India","availability":"sold-out","minPrice":180,"imageUrl":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1531415074968-036ba1b575da?w=1200&h=500&fit=crop&q=80","description":"The greatest rivalry in cricket — India vs Pakistan at the T20 World Cup. This match transcends sport. Played in front of 68,000 passionate fans at the iconic Eden Gardens in Kolkata, every India-Pakistan World Cup fixture produces moments that are talked about for decades. The intensity, the skill and the sheer weight of expectation make this the most anticipated match in the global cricketing calendar. Officially sold out.","partners":[]},{"id":"24","slug":"t20-world-cup-2026-super-8-match","sport":"cricket","leagueSlug":"t20-world-cup","eventName":"T20 World Cup 2026 — Super 8 Match","league":"ICC T20 World Cup","date":"2026-03-05","time":"14:30","venue":"Wankhede Stadium","city":"Mumbai, India","availability":"low","minPrice":95,"imageUrl":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1531415074968-036ba1b575da?w=1200&h=500&fit=crop&q=80","description":"The T20 World Cup Super 8 stage raises the stakes as the tournament's top teams face off in a do-or-die format at Wankhede Stadium in Mumbai. Perched on the shores of the Arabian Sea, Wankhede is one of cricket's most iconic venues — the ground where India won the 2011 ODI World Cup. The Super 8 stage produces some of the most dramatic cricket imaginable as nations fight to reach the semi-finals.","partners":[{"partnerId":"footballticketnet","partnerName":"FootballTicketNet","partnerIcon":"⚽","price":95,"tag":"Best Price"},{"partnerId":"awin","partnerName":"Awin","partnerIcon":"🌐","price":108}]},{"id":"25","slug":"t20-world-cup-2026-final","sport":"cricket","leagueSlug":"t20-world-cup","eventName":"T20 World Cup 2026 — Final","league":"ICC T20 World Cup","date":"2026-03-15","time":"19:00","venue":"Narendra Modi Stadium","city":"Ahmedabad, India","availability":"sold-out","minPrice":250,"imageUrl":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1531415074968-036ba1b575da?w=1200&h=500&fit=crop&q=80","description":"The ICC T20 World Cup Final returns to the Narendra Modi Stadium for a fitting conclusion to the greatest short-format tournament on earth. Two nations, 20 overs each, and one chance to be crowned world champions. The final of a T20 World Cup delivers drama, nerves and pure entertainment in equal measure — and with 132,000 fans creating an atmosphere that shakes the ground, this is the ultimate cricket experience. Sold out.","partners":[]}],"title":"ICC T20 World Cup 2026 Events","sportIcon":"🏏","rounded":true}]}]]}],["$","footer",null,{"style":{"background":"var(--white)","borderTop":"1px solid var(--border-gray)","padding":"60px 40px 32px"},"children":[["$","div",null,{"style":{"maxWidth":"1280px","margin":"0 auto","paddingBottom":"40px","borderBottom":"1px solid var(--border-gray)"},"className":"footer-main-grid","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","div",null,{"style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-poppins, Poppi